column5: Mr. Arthur M.  Happy birthday to you, and to many more to come.
Happy belated b-day. Hope you had a great day.  Mike
105..is that like dog years..so divide by 7 carry the 4..ahhh never was to good at math  have a great day
I can't believe he's lived this long without me killing him!  Bex (Joe's loving wife   )
105  He's in pretty good shape for and ole man and a plumber to boot!   Happy Birthday !  Whopper
it is because his plumbing works that he has lived to be that old!... might be he little blue pills too... I dunno. I hear something rattling when he jogs along.   Gerritt.
Ohhh shiz... Happy Birthday brother!   Gerritt
Have a very happy birthday Art
Good to see you finally caught up to me Bud. Have a good one and a tip of the Pepsi can to ya!
I do remember him saying that you surprised him once on his birthday with a car... but you missed!  105 ain't squat!.. I feel like I'm 501 right now...  Happy Birthday and Best Fishes Art!!!
hmmmm 105...so thats what like 173 canadian right? someones getting old... Happy birthday ART! may you have many more
Happy Birthday Art  Pam
Is that in dog years.  Have a good one, happy birthday.
Have a happy...go fishing...but don't forget to duck, and bob and weave your way to the truck  Maureen
Must be doing something right, keep at it!  A very happy birthday to you!

Hey cool, our birthdays are only one day apart  From one Taurus to another, Happy Birthday Art!!!  Hope you have a great day and that no good brother of yours takes you out fishing or something  Cheers,  Joey
Happy Birthday,Art have yourself a great day bud...oh by the way,stay away from the chicken coop.  Steve

A taurus? Dat's bull! Have a great day Art. Both you Sudden twins are some of the nicest people on this board. I really hope you have the best day.  ps. At Lakair this year would it kill you plumbers to bring and USE a little crack patch?
Happy Birthday Art! you aren`t nearly as old as I feel.

Thanks all for the well wishes I think I will go down to the boat and see if I can get a few catfish to bite. Bec's only wishes I was 105 but to bad it is only 45 so she has a long time to put up with me.......   Art
Happy Birthdays to Art and Joey...  I hope you both get what you like or like what you get...
Happy Birthday Art !
Happy Birthday to you, Happy birthday to you, Happy birthday dear Art, Happy birthday to you...  I figure you never age beyond 39, so you are still very young!  Enjoy your special day!  Cheers,  Jen
Have a great birthday! At 105, you must have caught a lot of fish? And many more.  Easton

Happy BD, you ole plumma, you.  I think that Roy is talking about Crack Spackle, the Plumma's Friend.  Pretty darn sure that a little lotion before application of the crack spackle would assist ( ! ) with the removal.  Good luck with all of that.
"so if your canyon is open for yodeling"....thats damn funny there!Crack Spackle,works for me! Joe
A belated happy birthday to you Art...  And to you too Joey... hope you's had a good one...  See you's at Lakair...
Happy bday ya old fArt
